<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 14:06:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>教育部因阿拉伯以色列东道主而撤回对犹太活动的资助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/israeli-education-ministry-withdraws-funding-of-jewish-event-over-arab-israeli-host/0000018d-1216-d94e-abcf-3bf65cd70000</link><description>“代表异族通婚的女性不能代表犹太文化”，该部在谈到记者兼主持人露西·阿哈里什时表示，她的丈夫是犹太法乌达明星查希·哈勒维。主办“促进多元化、进步和自由犹太教”年度活动的以色列理事会要求该部撤回其决定</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 12:43:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/israeli-education-ministry-withdraws-funding-of-jewish-event-over-arab-israeli-host/0000018d-1216-d94e-abcf-3bf65cd70000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日100天后，加沙边境社区的以色列居民再也无法抑制愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/100-days-after-oct-7-israeli-residents-of-gaza-communities-cannot-hold-back-their-anger/0000018d-119f-d71c-ad9f-539f6aa70000</link><description>“你抛弃了我们直至死亡，我们的世界在你的注视下化为尘土” ■ 饱受蹂躏的加沙边境基布兹的“愤怒”幸存者聚集在以色列议会外，要求政府辞职</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 11:59:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/100-days-after-oct-7-israeli-residents-of-gaza-communities-cannot-hold-back-their-anger/0000018d-119f-d71c-ad9f-539f6aa70000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列军队决定给出详细答复时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/when-the-israeli-army-decides-to-give-a-detailed-answer/0000018d-11de-dac4-a9cf-53ffa52b0000</link><description>在战争期间经常发生的爆炸房屋内有居住者的情况中，以色列国防军倾向于保持含糊不清以掩盖“附带损害”的严重程度</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 11:21:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/when-the-israeli-army-decides-to-give-a-detailed-answer/0000018d-11de-dac4-a9cf-53ffa52b0000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特：伊朗利用以色列人拍摄安全官员的家，影响公众</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-iran-used-israelis-to-photo-security-officials-homes-influence-the-public/0000018d-0ed6-db13-affd-7ff79e500000</link><description>《辛贝特》证实了《国土报》的调查，调查显示伊朗情报机构运营煽动以色列人相互对抗、甚至招募以色列人的团体和页面，并揭露了至少另外三人</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:38:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-iran-used-israelis-to-photo-security-officials-homes-influence-the-public/0000018d-0ed6-db13-affd-7ff79e500000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗称袭击了以色列驻伊拉克“摩萨德总部”，为加沙战争中“其指挥官被杀”报仇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/iran-says-it-attacked-israel-mossad-hq-in-iraq-to-avenge-the-killings-of-its-commanders/0000018d-116d-d71c-ad9f-53ef2bb80000</link><description>在伊朗声称摧毁了位于埃尔比勒的“摩萨德间谍总部”后，美国和法国谴责这次袭击是对伊拉克半自治库尔德斯坦主权的“鲁莽”和“令人担忧的侵犯”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:06:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/iran-says-it-attacked-israel-mossad-hq-in-iraq-to-avenge-the-killings-of-its-commanders/0000018d-116d-d71c-ad9f-53ef2bb80000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争期间，以色列的民主衰落并未停止。在很多方面情况变得更糟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-gaza-war-hasnt-stopped-israels-democratic-decline-in-many-ways-it-made-it-worse/0000018d-0dd4-d71c-ad9f-4fd64c7b0000</link><description>更多的监控、更多的枪支、更少的言论自由：内塔尼亚胡的联盟在 10 月 7 日的袭击后停止了削弱司法机构的计划，但战争却让它在没有这些的情况下实现了许多目标</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 09:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-gaza-war-hasnt-stopped-israels-democratic-decline-in-many-ways-it-made-it-worse/0000018d-0dd4-d71c-ad9f-4fd64c7b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/idf-releases-name-of-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-1181-de9c-a3df-7bf982c90001</link><description>21 岁的尼赞·谢斯勒 (Nitzan Schessler) 来自哈德拉 (Hadera)，周一在加沙南部的战斗中身亡。 37 岁的诺姆·阿什拉姆 (Noam Ashram) 周二因 12 月在加沙中部的战斗中受伤而死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 09:25:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/idf-releases-name-of-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-1181-de9c-a3df-7bf982c90001</guid></item><item><title>以色列延长紧急令，阻止被拘留的加沙人见律师</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-extends-emergency-order-preventing-detained-gazans-from-seeing-a-lawyer/0000018d-114c-d71c-ad9f-53ce280d0000</link><description>以色列议会还批准了延长紧急命令的一读，该命令允许极右翼国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本·格维尔降低巴勒斯坦安全囚犯的条件</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 08:54:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-extends-emergency-order-preventing-detained-gazans-from-seeing-a-lawyer/0000018d-114c-d71c-ad9f-53ce280d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列购买了一个大规模在线影响力系统来对抗反犹太主义和哈马斯暴行的否认</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-bought-mass-online-influence-system-to-counter-antisemitism-hamas-atrocity-denial/0000018d-0d31-db13-affd-7d3532830000</link><description>10 月 7 日后不久，国防、情报和民间机构意识到，他们正在输给据消息人士称哈马斯“运转良好的心理和信息战机器”的在线战斗。因此，尽管担心未来政治滥用，他们还是悄悄购买了数字工具来打击虚假信息</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 03:59:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-bought-mass-online-influence-system-to-counter-antisemitism-hamas-atrocity-denial/0000018d-0d31-db13-affd-7d3532830000</guid></item><item><title>拉法过境点也可能是巴勒斯坦权力机构返回加沙的路线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/rafah-border-crossing-may-also-be-the-route-for-the-palestinian-authoritys-return-to-gaza/0000018d-0f44-d71c-ad9f-4fc69f020000</link><description>埃及担心以色列对过境点的控制将剥夺开罗在加沙的关键影响力。将其移交给巴勒斯坦权力机构可能会减轻这些担忧并有助于恢复加沙地带的正常状态 - 但目前不太可能发生</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 03:59:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/rafah-border-crossing-may-also-be-the-route-for-the-palestinian-authoritys-return-to-gaza/0000018d-0f44-d71c-ad9f-4fc69f020000</guid></item><item><title>拉阿纳纳袭击可能预示着来自动荡的约旦河西岸的一波巴勒斯坦恐怖浪潮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/raanana-attack-could-herald-a-wave-of-palestinian-terror-from-volatile-west-bank/0000018d-0eeb-de9c-a3df-6ffb1e190000</link><description>经济危机还可能导致针对巴勒斯坦权力机构的暴力爆发——以色列国防军担心局势可能会恶化——但很难想象内塔尼亚胡会允许西岸工人进入该国 ■ 以色列正在逐步减少在加沙的军事存在，但无法在新的人质释放协议上取得进展</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 03:59:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/raanana-attack-could-herald-a-wave-of-palestinian-terror-from-volatile-west-bank/0000018d-0eeb-de9c-a3df-6ffb1e190000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟针对 10 月 7 日以色列袭击事件对哈马斯政治领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article-live/idf-grave-concern-for-lives-of-two-hostages-iran-claims-to-attack-mossad-hq-in-iraq/0000018d-1055-de9c-a3df-7bfd33c90000</link><description>以色列国防军周一公布在加沙阵亡的预备役士兵姓名；预备役士兵在加沙战斗中受伤身亡 ■ 以色列南部的一家商店被火箭弹击中 ■ 以色列国防军公布了据称“处于严重危险”的两名人质的姓名；拉阿纳纳袭击事件后，16 人仍在医院治疗。 ■ 伊朗表示，伊拉克和叙利亚发生的袭击旨在威慑安全威胁。 ■ 以色列国防军逮捕了拉阿纳纳恐怖袭击的嫌疑人；昨晚，27 名恐怖分子嫌疑人在约旦河西岸被捕 ■ 卡塔尔总理表示需要采取外交努力解决胡塞武装的侵略</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 03:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article-live/idf-grave-concern-for-lives-of-two-hostages-iran-claims-to-attack-mossad-hq-in-iraq/0000018d-1055-de9c-a3df-7bfd33c90000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在爱荷华州获胜演讲中表示，如果他是总统，哈马斯就不会攻击以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/trump-projected-iowa-caucus-winner-staking-early-claim-to-republican-nomination/0000018d-0fe5-db13-affd-7fe5f2bc0000</link><description>前总统击败对手赢得 2024 年首届共和党总统竞选</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 01:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/trump-projected-iowa-caucus-winner-staking-early-claim-to-republican-nomination/0000018d-0fe5-db13-affd-7fe5f2bc0000</guid></item><item><title>政府争执推迟向加沙地带哈马斯扣押的以色列人质支付工资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/government-spats-delay-salary-payments-for-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018d-0eea-db13-affd-7fef55340000</link><description>10 月 7 日后 100 多天，各部委之间关于如何支付俘虏工资的分歧仍未解决</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 22:33:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/government-spats-delay-salary-payments-for-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018d-0eea-db13-affd-7fef55340000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨的 MKs 对他向内塔尼亚胡及其极右翼盟友投降感到沮丧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/gantzs-mks-frustrated-with-his-capitulations-to-netanyahu-and-his-far-right-allies/0000018d-0ede-de9c-a3df-6fff3ed10000</link><description>几名政党议员表示，执政联盟中的其他政党曾多次利用其内阁多数席位来违反与民族团结的协议。一位人士表示，“我们总是在自己选择的战斗中失败”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 21:31:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/gantzs-mks-frustrated-with-his-capitulations-to-netanyahu-and-his-far-right-allies/0000018d-0ede-de9c-a3df-6fff3ed10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队通知两名哈马斯扣押人质的家人，严重关切他们的生命安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-notifies-families-of-two-hamas-held-hostages-of-grave-concern-for-their-lives/0000018d-0e9b-de9c-a3df-6ffb8f0f0000</link><description>“伊泰不是被我们部队射杀的，”以色列国防军发言人在哈马斯播放了伊泰和两名人质的视频一天后的新闻发布会上说。他补充说：“回想起来，我们知道我们袭击的目标就在他们被关押的地点附近。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 20:25:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-notifies-families-of-two-hamas-held-hostages-of-grave-concern-for-their-lives/0000018d-0e9b-de9c-a3df-6ffb8f0f0000</guid></item><item><title>两名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列军队炮火打死；士兵记录下将男子踢倒在地的记录</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-killed-by-idf-fire-in-west-bank-soldiers-seen-kicking-man-on-ground/0000018d-0e33-de9c-a3df-6ffbee730000</link><description>据报道，在与以色列军队的冲突中，一名 24 岁的妇女站在附近的一座建筑物上，被以色列国防军士兵开枪打死。在另一起事件中，一名巴勒斯坦男子被以色列国防军的炮火打死</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 19:36:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-killed-by-idf-fire-in-west-bank-soldiers-seen-kicking-man-on-ground/0000018d-0e33-de9c-a3df-6ffbee730000</guid></item><item><title>他们是犹太反犹太复国主义者，但他们不是巴勒斯坦事业的盟友</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-15/ty-article/.highlight/theyre-jewish-anti-zionists-but-theyre-no-ally-of-the-palestinian-cause/0000018d-0e48-d71c-ad9f-4fcaeb160000</link><description>巴勒斯坦运动不应该与 Neturei Karta 建立桥梁，后者的意识形态要求巴勒斯坦国是一个临时国家，无论他们多么愿意将自己标记化</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 19:19:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-15/ty-article/.highlight/theyre-jewish-anti-zionists-but-theyre-no-ally-of-the-palestinian-cause/0000018d-0e48-d71c-ad9f-4fcaeb160000</guid></item><item><title>“处于内爆的边缘”：以色列军队将精锐部队从加沙转移到约旦河西岸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/on-the-brink-of-implosion-israeli-army-transfers-elite-unit-out-of-gaza-to-west-bank/0000018d-0e2b-de9c-a3df-6ffbf7c90000</link><description>以色列国防军认为，该部队离开加沙是在加沙战斗中失去重要力量的原因，但认为在约旦河西岸局势升级之际，这是必要的。消息人士称，这可归因于政府未能决定改善巴勒斯坦财政状况的措施</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 18:30:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/on-the-brink-of-implosion-israeli-army-transfers-elite-unit-out-of-gaza-to-west-bank/0000018d-0e2b-de9c-a3df-6ffbf7c90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院撤销对在社交媒体上批评以色列国防军的高中教师的解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-reverses-dismissal-of-high-school-teacher-who-criticized-idf-on-social-media/0000018d-0dbd-d71c-ad9f-4fbfe0390000</link><description>法官裁定市政府没有提供解雇的正当理由，并补充说哈马斯袭击和加沙战争不会改变“教师言论自由的界限”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 18:20:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-reverses-dismissal-of-high-school-teacher-who-criticized-idf-on-social-media/0000018d-0dbd-d71c-ad9f-4fbfe0390000</guid></item></channel></rss>